file=AI & Agents/edge/operational/skill/edge-skill-routing.md В· eвЂ”s:edge вЂ” Skill Routing (no identity layer вЂ” non-leader)=```\ncandidate (scout, operator, any agent) в”Ђshape testв”Ђв–є forge (AI methods) \| edge continues (tech/platforms)\nв””в–є tech-adoption-criteria (score, 0.6-flagged)\nв”њв”Ђbelow barв”Ђв–є watchlist-discipline (triggers + dates) в”Ђevents/re-checksв”Ђв–є re-score\nв””в”Ђabove barв”Ђв–є pilot-spec-handoff в”Ђв–є proto (cage) в”Ђverdict returnsв”Ђв–є adoption proposal (Rail 3) or watchlist update\nlandscape re-verify / operator domain selection в”Ђв–є landscape-assets (dated versions)\n```\n\nHandoffs out: forge (method-shaped) \В· proto (pilots) \В· scout (event radar in) \В· compliance function (regulatory axis input) \В· meta's fleet-governance (adoption proposals) \В· operator (domain selection, bar setting).\nPrecedence: returned verdicts > re-checks > new scoring > landscape maintenance.\n